Class ShrBirtView

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.View

    public abstract class ShrBirtView
extends org.springframework.web.servlet.view.AbstractView
    This class is an helper for interfacing with BIRT reporting tools. Is is built with the goal to keep SprHibRAD away to have BIRT in its class path. The application code, instead, must have it, because is the application code that will invoke the BIRT APIs.
